elements indexentry indexentry Element
indexentry &indexentry.purpose;
&indexentry.synopsis.gen; Description
An IndexEntry wraps all of the index terms associated with a particular primary index term. This includes an arbitrary list of secondary and tertiary elements as well as See and SeeAlso elements.
Processing expectations
&format.block; A rendered index usually places secondary items under primary items and tertiary items under secondary.
&indexentry.parents.gen; &indexentry.children.gen;
See Also &indexentry.seealso.gen;
